      </p>
      <a class="btn octopus" href={OCTOPUS_REFERRAL} rel="noopener"><span aria-hidden="true">🐙</span> Claim the £50 referral</a>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:1rem">share.octopus.energy/lush-spark-49</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
